Here is a weekly meal plan for a 45 year old male that will promote fat loss and muscle gain:

Breakfast

Oatmeal with berries and nuts
Hard-boiled eggs
Yogurt with fruit and granola
Avocado toast
Lunch

Salad with grilled chicken or fish
Leftovers from dinner
Sandwich on whole-wheat bread
Soup
Dinner

Salmon with roasted vegetables
Chicken stir-fry
Veggie burger on a whole-wheat bun
Lentil soup
Snacks

Fruits and vegetables
Nuts and seeds
Hard-boiled eggs
Yogurt
Popcorn
Tips

Drink plenty of water.
Avoid processed foods and sugary drinks.
Eat plenty of fruits, vegetables, and whole grains.
Choose lean protein sources.
Be patient and consistent with your diet and exercise routine.
This meal plan provides a balanced diet that is high in protein, fiber, and healthy fats. It is also low in calories and sugar. By following this meal plan, you can promote fat loss and muscle gain.

It is important to note that everyone's body is different and what works for one person may not work for another. It is important to experiment with different diets and exercise routines to find what works best for you.
